skdetail:

Invocation Name: my quotes
des:
Start your day with quotes that help you reflect on life Challenges. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
